{"tid":1820052,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【一人一句支持國難忠醫】要手足！！！！","createTime":"2020-01-11T09:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T14:38:26.000Z","uid":220018,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"76e42007578df4392fe7ac0685afebcb0e8cce91","tid":1820052,"uid":220018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"呢半年，人道救援最大組織國難忠醫Channel<br />\n早兩日Admin「林鄭都係咁」被消失。<br />\n詳情：【還原】國難忠醫被消失事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1818873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1818873</a><br />\n<br />\n剩返低嘅細牛醫一人獨撐場面，<br />\n搵埋「林鄭都係咁」媽媽開記招。<br />\n仲出現到香港人面前，但佢地已經心力交瘁。<br />\n諗吓被消失嘅「林鄭都係咁」？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係無法想像呀！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明唔明點解要高調出黎記招，要煲大佢呀！<br />\n今日個個淨係理台灣大選？<br />\n係呀，小英一定要贏，<br />\n咁香港人呢？未贏呀，仲有好多被消失！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">手足一個不能少，何況係救援醫師？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n好多人可能都接受過忠醫救助，<br />\n但呢個時候都唔想增加醫師們嘅負擔。<br />\n唔敢主動煩佢地，我地團結集中啦！<br />\n<br />\n係呢度，放低你嘅支持，比佢地知道<br />\n香港人，全部都撐醫師。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd3f262e62c1e66b197f5d3171fa5629233e606","tid":1820052,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWQEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=84089b14\" data-auto-link ta